  "longBusinessSummary": "Companhia Brasileira de Alum\u00ednio produces and sells aluminum products. The company provides bauxite, hydrate, alumina, molten aluminum, ingots, secondary ingots, slabs, billets, rod, caster rolls, caster sheet and coils, hot-rolled sheet and coils, roofing and siding, foil, coated foil, extruded profiles, surface treatment lines, custom parts, and components and services. It also owns and operates hydroelectric power plants. The company serves e automotive, building and construction, energy, agribusiness, consumer goods, packaging, transportation, and other industries. It operates in Brazil, South America, North America, and Europe. Companhia Brasileira de Alum\u00ednio was incorporated in 1941 and is headquartered in S\u00e3o Paulo, Brazil. Companhia Brasileira de Alum\u00ednio operates as a subsidiary of Votorantim S.A.",
